    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know about the hotlines. i've called them. they just say the same scripted things. it feels like they’re just trying to keep the noise going instead of actually solving anything. it’s like my misery is just this constant, chaotic energy that never stops bleeding into everything around me. i feel like a black hole of just... badness. it's exhausting to even try to be \"okay\" when it feels like i'm just polluting the air with my struggle. does that even make sense? that i'm just a source of entropy?",
